# Modulo people

Escopo
- Gestao de colaboradores (workers/employees).
- Cadastro, atualizacao e listagem por workspace.

Rotas e entradas
- Stack: `src/modules/people/presentation/stacks/people.stack.tsx`.
- Base path: `/people`.
- Pages:
  - `landing`: `presentation/pages/landing/landing.page`.
  - `home`: `presentation/pages/home/home.page`.

Modelos principais
- `EmployeeModel`: id, firstName, lastName, email, phone, role, department, hiredAt, salaryCents, active, createdAt.
- `EmployeeStatus`: active | inactive | on_leave.

Services
- `people.service.ts`
  - `listEmployees()` tenta backend e cai para mock se necessario.
  - `createEmployee()` cria via API quando workspaceId existe.
  - `updateEmployee()` usa `usersAuthService` + workspace.
  - Mapeia formatos da API para `EmployeeModel`.
- `people-api.ts`
  - Endpoints `/people/workers` e `/people/internal/workspaces/{id}/workers`.

Integracoes
- Depende de `companyService` para workspaceId.
- Depende de `usersAuthService` para userUid.
- Integrado com schedule e work-order (alocacao de trabalhadores).

Guardrails
- Sempre validar workspaceId quando chamar API.
- Evitar duplicar logica de mapeamento fora do service.
